  "time_ut": 1657733887,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'The problem of Tamil people also needs to be solved'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The religious leaders have jointly emphasized that all the parliamentary representatives should come together and take a decisive decision to propose a solution to the problem of the Tamil people in the current crisis.",
        "The religious leaders have jointly emphasized in a special media meeting held today at Nallai Thirunnasambandar Atheenam.",
        "In this regard, in their further statement, the religious leaders said that all the Tamil parties and especially the Tamil parliamentarians should come together soon and decide what the decision should be taken in today's Sri Lankan political environment. In this regard, they further stated,",
        "This is the moment when Tamil parliamentarians and party leaders, regardless of whether they are from the north-east, the hills or the south, overcome their differences and come together for the people. So get together and investigate with a wise vision. It is the imperative of time. At this time you will refuse to come together and investigate but it will be a great historical mistake.",
        "In this media meeting, Nallai Atheena Guru Principal Somasundara Paramacharya Swami, Jaffa Diocese Bishop Justin Paynat Gnanaprakasam, Thellippa Durgadevi Devasthanam President Kalanithi Aru. Thirumurugan and Rishi Thondunatha Swamy were present. (a)"
      ],
